{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/if-you-dont-pay-your-tax-bill.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/if-you-dont-pay-your-tax-bill","title":"If you don't pay your tax bill","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T22:46:43+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2374","business_proposition":false,"description":"If you don't pay your tax bill, HM Revenue & Customs will choose a way to make you pay - find out what they can do","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>HM Revenue &amp; Customs (<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>) will take ‘enforcement action’ to get the money - you may be able to avoid this if you contact them.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>There are a number of ways <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> can get the tax you owe. These are called &lsquo;enforcement actions&rsquo;.</p>\n\n<p>They can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>ask debt collectors to get the money from you</li>\n  <li>collect what you owe through your wages or pension (if you owe less than £3,000)</li>\n  <li>take things you own and sell them (if you live in England, Wales or Northern Ireland) - this is called &lsquo;distraint&rsquo;</li>\n  <li>take you to court</li>\n  <li>make you bankrupt or close down your business</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> has further guidance on <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/payinghmrc/problems/dontpay/debts.htm\" title=\"What could happen if you don't pay HMRC\">enforcement actions.</a></p>\n\n<h2>Avoid enforcement action</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/difficulties-paying-hmrc/youve-missed-the-payment-deadline\" title=\"What to do if you can't pay your tax bill\">Contact <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr></a> as soon as you can - you may be able to either:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>get more time to pay</li>\n  <li>pay in instalments</li>\n</ul>\n\n","alternative_title":"If you ignore your tax bill"},"tags":[{"title":"Self Assessment","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax%2Fself-assessment.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes filing, deadlines, pay and tax records","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fself-assessment","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/self-assessment"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Directgov","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/directgov.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=directgov","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/directgov"},"parent":null}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/self-assessment-tax-return-deadlines.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/self-assessment-tax-return-deadlines","title":"Self Assessment deadlines 2011 to 2012 tax year","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-31T14:16:55+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/difficulties-paying-hmrc.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/difficulties-paying-hmrc","title":"If you can't pay your tax bill on time","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-10-22T22:46:27+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/self-assessment-tax-returns.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/self-assessment-tax-returns","title":"Self Assessment tax returns     ","format":"guide","updated_at":"2012-12-13T16:44:27+00